<span style="font-weight: 400;">This meditation opens your mind to the things happening around you- the feelings, smell, and activities.</span>

<b>Focused meditation</b>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">Unlike the mindfulness meditation, youâ€™ll put your mind on a single thing. It could be your breath, a mantra, a physical material. The idea is to focus and move away from distractions.</span>

<b>Guided meditation</b>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">Here youâ€™ll use your visualization power to create a picture of when you are feeling calmer.</span>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">Above all, domestic abuse survivor should utilize the power of meditation to break free from the emotional torture.</span>

