<b>Treatment</b>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">Medical professionals would often recommend you painkillers for instant relief. However, one should stop using them as soon they get rid of a tension headache. Excessive consumption of the same is found to be harmful. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">

