<span style="font-weight: 400;">According to her, the main cause of Irritable bowel syndrome is: </span><b>Gut-level fear, dread, anxiety. Griping and grunting.</b>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">One of the ways of healing this is through saying or writing affirmations.Â </span>

