<span style="font-weight: 400;">It is a potentially lethal ailment that ruptures oneâ€™s ability to breathe normally. This also causes growth of tumors that poses hurdles for a person to breathe.</span>

<b>Symptoms</b>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">For most people suffering from lung cancer, the symptoms occur only after the disease has reached a later stage. For others, the symptoms seem like that of a regular illness:</span>
<ul>
 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â Â Â Â Â </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Loss of appetite</span></li>
 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â Â Â Â Â </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Wheezing</span></li>
 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â Â Â Â Â </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Anxiety</span></li>
 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â Â Â Â Â </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Nausea</span></li>
 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â Â Â Â Â </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Fatigue</span></li>
 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â Â Â Â Â </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Recurrent headaches</span></li>
 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â Â Â Â Â </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Change of voice</span></li>
 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â Â Â Â Â </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Breathlessness</span></li>
 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â Â Â Â Â </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Frequent viral infection</span></li>
</ul>
<span style="font-weight: 400;">With time, if these are left unattended, severe indicators may then be visible. These include:</span>
<ul>
 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â Â Â Â Â </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Severe chest pain</span></li>
 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â Â Â Â Â </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Bone pain</span></li>
 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â Â Â Â Â </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Coughing out of blood</span></li>
</ul>
<b>Causes</b>
<ul>
 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â Â Â Â Â </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Smoking</span></li>
