</ul>
<b>What to eat?</b>

<span style="font-weight: 400;">A healthy diet could be your weapon against any ailment. Here are a few things you must have to fight lung cancer:</span>
<ul>
 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â Â Â Â Â </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Low-fat dairy products</span></li>
 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â Â Â Â Â </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Fruit and vegetable juices</span></li>
 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â Â Â Â Â </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Rice</span></li>
 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â Â Â Â Â </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Oatmeal</span></li>
 	<li><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Â Â Â Â Â </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Asparagus root</span></li>
